overview: This is the second in a series of the best barebacking moments captured on film at GAE Boy Video. This film features GAE boys Kyle, Ryan, Daniel, James, Matthew & Anthony. It's raw, uncensored, unedited and is some of the hottest action we've ever filmed. Contains two scenes previously released in the films Seattle College Boyz and Seattle Navy Boyz.
title: Seattle Bareback Boyz: Volume II
